<i>good about FR and four-wheel drive.</i></b></font>

61
00:04:26,874 --> 00:04:29,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Nakazato... one of the Night Kids.</b></font>

62
00:04:29,944 --> 00:04:32,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's your name?</b></font>

63
00:04:32,214 --> 00:04:34,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi Fujiwara.</b></font>

64
00:04:34,714 --> 00:04:37,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll remember that.</b></font>

65
00:04:37,454 --> 00:04:40,044
