148
00:10:25,404 --> 00:10:26,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cause it sure wasn't like this</i></b></font>

149
00:10:26,934 --> 00:10:29,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>when I made the deliveries this morning!</i></b></font>

150
00:10:29,434 --> 00:10:31,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now I get it!</i></b></font>

151
00:10:31,044 --> 00:10:34,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's why he was out before!</i>
<i>He was working on this!</i></b></font>

152
00:10:34,074 --> 00:10:35,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't know why...</i></b></font>

153
00:10:35,744 --> 00:10:38,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But anyway, it does feel</i>
<i>a whole lot better this way!</i></b></font>

154
00:10:38,114 --> 00:10:41,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Because it doesn't slide too much...</i>
<i>I can push it all the way!</i></b></font>

155
00:10:50,324 --> 00:10:52,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yow!
--Amazing!</b></font>

156
00:10:52,164 --> 00:10:54,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's some un-freakin'-believable drifting!</b></font>

157
00:11:07,674 --> 00:11:11,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the first time I've seen a guy
drift all the way through that corner!</b></font>

158
00:11:11,414 --> 00:11:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, he's nuts!</b></font>

159
00:11:12,884 --> 00:11:16,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'd never be able to do it if he didn't
have total mastery over his speed!</b></font>

160
00:11:17,454 --> 00:11:18,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck was that?!</b></font>

161
00:11:18,784 --> 00:11:21,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's no kind of drift I've ever seen before!</b></font>

162
00:11:21,524 --> 00:11:24,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible! That's drifting I'll never forget!</b></font>

163
00:11:24,024 --> 00:11:25,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, oh, man!</b></font>

164
00:11:50,654 --> 00:11:54,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is still on the R32's tail!</b></font>

165
00:11:54,294 --> 00:11:55,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's doing it!</b></font>

166
00:11:55,754 --> 00:11:58,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looks like Takumi's sticking
right behind the R32!</b></font>

167
00:11:58,324 --> 00:11:59,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mind-blowing!</b></font>

168
00:11:59,824 --> 00:12:01,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, Nakazato's an ace...</b></font>

169
00:12:01,364 --> 00:12:03,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Line him up with Ryosuke
Takahashi, another superstar,</b></font>

170
00:12:03,694 --> 00:12:07,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and you got a battle royal brewing already!</b></font>

171
00:12:07,234 --> 00:12:09,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And my best friend's racing against
both of 'em?! Unbelievable!</b></font>

172
00:12:09,704 --> 00:12:13,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, that is too cool!</b></font>

173
00:12:13,404 --> 00:12:15,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, yeah, but...</b></font>

174
00:12:15,414 --> 00:12:18,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Ryosuke Takahashi and his
FC aren't even in the race.</b></font>

175
00:12:18,944 --> 00:12:22,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's acting more like a third-person witness.</b></font>

176
00:12:22,254 --> 00:12:25,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right. Takumi's up against Nakazato here.</b></font>

177
00:12:25,284 --> 00:12:28,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His R32 has the Eight-Six at a disadvantage...</b></font>

178
00:12:28,254 --> 00:12:30,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But with Takumi at the wheel,
the Eight Six'll pull through in the end!</b></font>

179
00:12:30,724 --> 00:12:32,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, yeah. Takumi will take it, for sure!</b></font>

180
00:12:32,764 --> 00:12:35,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right, guys!</b></font>

181
00:12:52,644 --> 00:12:55,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's creeping further and further away!</b></font>

182
00:12:55,214 --> 00:12:57,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato's got a big mouth,</b></font>

183
00:12:57,454 --> 00:12:59,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it looks like he's got
the skill to back it up!</b></font>

184
00:12:59,454 --> 00:13:01,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look at how he distributes the load,</b></font>

185
00:13:01,394 --> 00:13:04,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>subduing the understeer while driving!</b></font>

186
00:13:04,194 --> 00:13:06,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He really knows how to
draw out the GT-R's power.</b></font>

187
00:13:06,894 --> 00:13:08,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not pretty to look at...</b></font>

188
00:13:08,594 --> 00:13:10,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is not the time to take it easy.</b></font>

189
00:13:10,904 --> 00:13:12,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, bro...</b></font>

190
00:13:12,404 --> 00:13:14,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whose side are you on, anyway?!</b></font>

191
00:13:14,874 --> 00:13:18,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the kid loses this one, it's all over!</b></font>

192
00:13:18,174 --> 00:13:20,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The real contest is only about to begin.</b></font>

193
00:13:20,074 --> 00:13:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first half has comparatively
more long straightaways...</b></font>

194
00:13:22,674 --> 00:13:24,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lots of gentle slopes, too.</b></font>

195
00:13:24,344 --> 00:13:26,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are lots of
disadvantages for the Eight-Six.</b></font>

196
00:13:26,744 --> 00:13:29,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the inclines are gonna start
getting rougher right around here.</b></font>

197
00:13:29,214 --> 00:13:32,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Perfect for a downhill
specialist to strut his stuff!</b></font>

198
00:13:49,534 --> 00:13:51,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All right! This kind of low-gear hairpin curve</i></b></font>

199
00:13:51,704 --> 00:13:53,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is right up the R32's alley!</i></b></font>

200
00:13:53,974 --> 00:13:57,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All I gotta do is cut my speed</i>
<i>by slamming on the brakes...</i></b></font>

201
00:14:02,014 --> 00:14:05,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Going downhill, like it or not, the front</i>
<i>wheels still have to bear the load,</i></b></font>

202
00:14:05,584 --> 00:14:08,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so its weakest point, the pushing</i>
<i>understeer, hardly occurs.</i></b></font>

203
00:14:08,694 --> 00:14:11,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Furthermore, accelerating from a low gear</i></b></font>

204
00:14:11,064 --> 00:14:14,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is what this car does better than any other!</i></b></font>

205
00:14:14,094 --> 00:14:16,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The fastest machine on the racing circuit...</i></b></font>

206
00:14:16,564 --> 00:14:18,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...is the toughest machine even on open roads!</i></b></font>

207
00:14:21,034 --> 00:14:23,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The R emblem on the rear</i></b></font>

208
00:14:23,404 --> 00:14:25,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is the legendary symbol for invincibility!</i></b></font>

209
00:14:25,904 --> 00:14:28,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Can you get close enough to read it?!</i></b></font>

210
00:14:35,414 --> 00:14:37,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Iketani...</b></font>

211
00:14:37,084 --> 00:14:38,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

212
00:14:38,454 --> 00:14:41,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been thinking.</b></font>

213
00:14:41,724 --> 00:14:43,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'Till now, I thought Takumi</b></font>

214
00:14:43,354 --> 00:14:45,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>was just a unique racer</b></font>

215
00:14:45,264 --> 00:14:48,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who's fast only when he's racing on Akina.</b></font>

216
00:14:48,764 --> 00:14:50,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if he raced on a different mountain pass,</b></font>

217
00:14:50,764 --> 00:14:53,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>how well would he drive?</b></font>

218
00:14:53,104 --> 00:14:54,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you wonder about that?</b></font>

219
00:14:54,604 --> 00:14:58,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, sure, I've mulled it over...</b></font>

220
00:14:58,304 --> 00:15:00,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But right now, all I'm thinking
about is the battle at hand!</b></font>

221
00:15:00,974 --> 00:15:02,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Win, Takumi!</b></font>

222
00:15:02,574 --> 00:15:04,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

223
00:15:21,764 --> 00:15:23,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, man!</i></b></font>

224
00:15:23,094 --> 00:15:25,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My eyes can't keep up with him!</i></b></font>

225
00:15:27,234 --> 00:15:30,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Looks like he's finally kicking out the jams!</i></b></font>

226
00:15:30,204 --> 00:15:33,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His inside tires are gripping the rim of the road!</i></b></font>

227
00:15:37,114 --> 00:15:40,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the one! The trick that I lost to!</i></b></font>

228
00:15:40,544 --> 00:15:43,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Didn't think I'd ever get</i>
<i>the chance to see it again!</i></b></font>

229
00:15:50,794 --> 00:15:53,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ryosuke's stopped with the chatter.</i></b></font>

230
00:15:53,124 --> 00:15:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Meaning there's no time for that now?</i></b></font>

231
00:15:56,064 --> 00:15:58,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've ridden shotgun with him tons of times...</i></b></font>

232
00:15:58,704 --> 00:16:02,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But this is the first time I've</i>
<i>seen him driving like this!</i></b></font>

233
00:16:02,374 --> 00:16:04,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never seen him so serious!</i></b></font>

234
00:16:04,304 --> 00:16:07,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Akina Skate Center"</b></font>

235
00:16:13,014 --> 00:16:14,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Getting closer...?!</i></b></font>

236
00:16:14,654 --> 00:16:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six is catching up to me?!</i></b></font>

237
00:16:17,014 --> 00:16:18,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Impossible!</i></b></font>

238
00:16:49,214 --> 00:16:52,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Brilliant! Catching up to me after all that...</i></b></font>

239
00:16:52,454 --> 00:16:55,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All my prejudices about the</i>
<i>Eight-Six being a 10-year-old car</i></b></font>

240
00:16:55,294 --> 00:16:56,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>have just been blown away!</i></b></font>

241
00:16:56,954 --> 00:17:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's a first-rate fighting machine!</i></b></font>

242
00:17:03,234 --> 00:17:05,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Okay, the kid gloves are off!</i></b></font>

243
00:17:05,164 --> 00:17:07,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Man, this is the best rush I've had in ages!</i></b></font>

244
00:17:07,904 --> 00:17:10,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In fact, this has gotta be the</i>
<i>hottest road race I've been in</i></b></font>

245
00:17:10,734 --> 00:17:12,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>since getting this car!</i></b></font>

246
00:17:50,714 --> 00:17:53,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>When it comes to hairpin turns,</i></b></font>

247
00:17:53,584 --> 00:17:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>he can't match the R32!</i></b></font>

248
00:17:56,554 --> 00:17:58,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how close the</i>
<i>Eight-Six sticks to the R32,</i></b></font>

249
00:17:58,584 --> 00:18:01,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the distance between them</i>
<i>always widens after a hairpin!</i></b></font>

250
00:18:01,724 --> 00:18:03,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Man, that Nakazato's got guts, too...</i></b></font>

251
00:18:03,954 --> 00:18:08,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Attacking the road like that,</i>
<i>downhill in a heavy-ass R32!</i></b></font>

252
00:18:51,744 --> 00:18:53,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wha-What the...?!</i></b></font>

253
00:18:55,514 --> 00:18:58,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six closed the gap</i>
<i>at the high-speed corner?!</i></b></font>

254
00:18:58,714 --> 00:19:01,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Going over 100 kilometers an hour</i>
<i>while doing a four-wheel drift</i></b></font>

255
00:19:01,884 --> 00:19:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>close enough to graze the guardrail?!</i></b></font>

256
00:19:04,354 --> 00:19:08,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't think any of it has to do</i>
<i>with the car's capabilities!</i></b></font>

257
00:19:08,294 --> 00:19:11,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That guy... has got a screw loose!</i></b></font>

258
00:19:11,794 --> 00:19:15,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If he makes one slip-up, he's roadkill for sure!</i></b></font>

259
00:19:15,364 --> 00:19:17,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But now I understand his secret!</i></b></font>

260
00:19:17,964 --> 00:19:19,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With a lightweight like the</i>
<i>Eight-Six, if he loses speed once,</i></b></font>

261
00:19:19,534 --> 00:19:23,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it takes like forever to get it back up again.</i></b></font>

262
00:19:23,034 --> 00:19:26,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He never lets himself lose a fraction</i>
<i>of speed more than he has to!</i></b></font>

263
00:19:26,704 --> 00:19:28,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now I finally get why,</i></b></font>

264
00:19:28,244 --> 00:19:29,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>when I raced against him,</i></b></font>

265
00:19:29,914 --> 00:19:33,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>he could always catch up to me,</i>
<i>no matter how many times I lost him!</i></b></font>

266
00:19:38,324 --> 00:19:40,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Crap!</i></b></font>

267
00:20:06,214 --> 00:20:07,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't shake him!</i></b></font>

268
00:20:07,954 --> 00:20:09,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just the opposite!</i></b></font>

269
00:20:09,084 --> 00:20:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's hanging on to me for</i>
<i>longer and longer periods!</i></b></font>

270
00:20:12,124 --> 00:20:15,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The bastard... is tough!</i></b></font>

271
00:20:29,434 --> 00:20:34,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nakazato's clearing the guardrail</i>
<i>by a good 20-30 centimeters.</i></b></font>

272
00:20:34,274 --> 00:20:36,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how fast you are,</i></b></font>

273
00:20:36,214 --> 00:20:38,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that's about right.</i></b></font>

274
00:20:38,214 --> 00:20:39,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yet the Eight-Six's bumper</i></b></font>

275
00:20:39,744 --> 00:20:44,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is almost close enough</i>
<i>to the rail to make sparks!</i></b></font>

276
00:20:44,484 --> 00:20:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That guy's in a league of his own!</i></b></font>

277
00:20:46,384 --> 00:20:49,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How?! How can he control a drift</i>
<i>with that kind of precision?!</i></b></font>

278
00:21:03,334 --> 00:21:08,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Since I've been steering</i>
<i>hard and using the ABS,</i></b></font>

279
00:21:08,074 --> 00:21:13,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the load on the front tires has</i>
<i>been a lot heavier than I thought!</i></b></font>

280
00:21:13,084 --> 00:21:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This race is suddenly getting</i>
<i>much more challenging!</i></b></font>

281
00:21:42,144 --> 00:21:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The five hairpins are coming up...</b></font>

282
00:21:45,584 --> 00:21:48,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's where he left you in the dust.</b></font>

283
00:21:48,954 --> 00:21:51,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I bet that's gonna be
a key point this time, too.</b></font>

284
00:21:58,064 --> 00:22:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An R32 versus an Eight-Six...</i></b></font>

285
00:22:00,464 --> 00:22:02,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Who would've thought the</i>
<i>battle would be this fierce?</i></b></font>

286
00:22:02,764 --> 00:22:05,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Both of those cars are</i>
<i>being taken to their limits.</i></b></font>

287
00:22:05,034 --> 00:22:07,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But which one of them</i>
<i>is gonna take the prize?!</i></b></font>

288
00:22:16,044 --> 00:22:19,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm at the hairpins! And I can hear 'em coming!</b></font>

289
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
